<main>
    <section id="hero" class="particle-container">
        <div class="hero-wrapper fade-in">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1 class="hero-text">Creativity is not a talent,<br class="hero-break"> itâ€™s a way of thinking.</h1>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="about" class="section fade-in block">
        <div class="section-wrapper fade-in">
            <div class="section-header">
                <p class="section-name">About</p>
                <h2 class="section-title">A new perspective.</h2>
                <hr class="section-underline">
            </div>
            <div class="section-content">
                <p>We are a creative intelligence consultancy delivering meaningful solutions to complex problems. We do this through transdisciplinary innovation, the cross-pollination of processes between knowledge-bases to form new ways of thinking.</p>
                <br>
                <p>As businesses navigate the increasing rate of change and complexity of systems indicative of an ever-increasing rate of change, new ways of thinking and doing are essential to not only thriving, but surviving.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="services" class="section fade-in">
        <div class="section-wrapper fade-in">
            <div class="section-header">
                <p class="section-name">Services</p>
                <h2 class="section-title">Section Title</h2>
                <hr class="section-underline">
            </div>
            <div class="section-content">
                <p>We're experts in:</p>
                <ul class="expertise">
                    <li class="expertise-item"><span class="material-icons">chevron_right</span>Creative processes</li>
                    <li class="expertise-item"><span class="material-icons">chevron_right</span>Problem solving</li>
                    <li class="expertise-item"><span class="material-icons">chevron_right</span>Facilitation</li>
                    <li class="expertise-item"><span class="material-icons">chevron_right</span>Innovation</li>
                    <li class="expertise-item"><span class="material-icons">chevron_right</span>Collaboration</li>
                    <li class="expertise-item"><span class="material-icons">chevron_right</span>Curiosity</li>
                    <li class="expertise-item"><span class="material-icons">chevron_right</span>Knowledge</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Because no two problems are the same, no two processes for solving a problem will be the same either. Our tailored service offerings are designed to be flexible and adaptable to meet your unique needs, meaningfully solving complex problems quickly and effectively.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="approach" class="section fade-in block">
        <div class="section-wrapper fade-in">
            <div class="section-header">
                <p class="section-name">Approach</p>
                <h2 class="section-title">Section Title</h2>
                <hr class="section-underline">
            </div>
            <div class="section-content">
                <p>Transdisciplinarity occurs when processes are shared across knowledge-bases to inform a more holistic approach, achieving a unity of knowledge that transcends disciplinary boundaries. This is how we solve complex problems.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="contact" class="section fade-in">
        <div class="section-wrapper fade-in">
            <div class="section-header">
                <p class="section-name">Contact</p>
                <h2 class="section-title">Let's get started.</h2>
                <hr class="section-underline">
            </div>
            <div class="section-content">
                <form action="/api/contact-form" method="GET" id="contact" autocomplete="off">
                    <label for="name" class="input-label">Name:</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-input fade-in" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Full Name">
                    <label for="email" class="input-label">Email:</label>
                    <input type="email" class="form-input fade-in" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Email">
                    <label for="phone" class="input-label">Phone:</label>
                    <input type="tel" class="form-input fade-in" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="Phone">
                    <textarea class="form-input fade-in" name="message" id="message" rows="4" placeholder="Message"></textarea>
                    <button type="submit" class="fade-in" id="submit">Submit</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>

